{"tid":736704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重冇乜野唔會炒車？","createTime":"2018-07-10T12:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T12:41:43.000Z","uid":41292,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"95013dd17b782611ab6cbf1f00b634d68fbea343","tid":736704,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"炒車通常<br />\n都係講緊一班人比一個人用一面之詞引導<br />\n去攻擊某啲人或者令到某個人受影響<br />\n好似葉希臨咁<br />\n幾時連時事都可以炒車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估錯左又點呀 影響到咩人呀？<br />\n好似泰國教練<br />\n人地都係估下估下 搵下資料咁姐<br />\n屌 郁啲又話人炒車 仲要係個post重覆幾廿次<br />\n方死人唔知自己估啱或者同條友唔同睇法咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到正正常常想睇下討論 個post一半都係到嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f226078dcec5e644ecc6576e611e82b2fbfa683","tid":736704,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2994022ae737474aea18612edae3edb809672be","tid":736704,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f226078dcec5e644ecc6576e611e82b2fbfa683","tid":736704,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"喺感情台要保持三日距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d8ddea822ae294f2b62e0a4e66a9f88ab7ef93","tid":736704,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a84af8906f780c17b7407e40d12d62d0a476bac","tid":736704,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96e06b8cdf92f592bf19c8c91e9df9a94864531","tid":736704,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:41:43.000Z